class_name EntityDexData
## World-threat creature roster, extracted from the Periliminal.Space
## Master OmniDex, plus a hand-authored Factionless roster. 150 entity forms
## per faction (600 total): LINES holds the 3-stage evolution lines (groups
## 1-8 per category, Stage 1 weakest / Stage 3 apex); SINGLE_STAGE_LINES
## holds the single-form legendaries (groups 9-12 per category) for
## SovereignCrown/VeiledCurrent/WildlandsAscendant; FACTIONLESS_LINES holds
## its own 3-stage lines (groups 1-8) plus 6 single-stage legendaries
## (group 9, one per category) to match the other three factions'
## per-faction total. Distinct from CompanionRoster (playable/collectible
## companions) — these are hostile/neutral entities encountered in the
## open world, faction-exclusive same as companions.
##
## FACTIONLESS_LINES is a hand-authored addition (not in the source doc)
## — ancient-pantheon-themed entities for players with no faction,
## with original coined names (inspired by archetype, not pantheon copies).
## More of the pantheon list remains unused for future lines.

